{
  "dashboard": {
    "id": null,
    "uid": "trisla-create-slices",
    "title": "TriSLA - Criar Slices (LNP & Templates)",
    "tags": ["trisla", "slices", "create", "lnp", "templates"],
    "style": "dark",
    "timezone": "browser",
    "refresh": "30s",
    "schemaVersion": 38,
    "version": 1,
    "templating": {
      "list": [
        {
          "name": "slice_type",
          "type": "query",
          "label": "Tipo de Slice",
          "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
          "current": {
            "selected": false,
            "text": "URLLC",
            "value": "URLLC"
          },
          "options": [
            {"text": "URLLC", "value": "URLLC", "selected": true},
            {"text": "eMBB", "value": "eMBB", "selected": false},
            {"text": "mMTC", "value": "mMTC", "selected": false}
          ],
          "query": {
            "query": "label_values(trisla_slices_active, slice_type)",
            "refId": "StandardVariableQuery"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "bandwidth",
          "type": "custom",
          "label": "Bandwidth (Mbps)",
          "current": {
            "selected": false,
            "text": "100",
            "value": "100"
          },
          "options": [
            {"text": "50", "value": "50"},
            {"text": "100", "value": "100", "selected": true},
            {"text": "200", "value": "200"},
            {"text": "500", "value": "500"},
            {"text": "1000", "value": "1000"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "latency",
          "type": "custom",
          "label": "Latência (ms)",
          "current": {
            "selected": false,
            "text": "1",
            "value": "1"
          },
          "options": [
            {"text": "1", "value": "1", "selected": true},
            {"text": "5", "value": "5"},
            {"text": "10", "value": "10"},
            {"text": "50", "value": "50"}
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    "panels": [
      {
        "id": 1,
        "title": "Criar Slice via API",
        "type": "text",
        "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0},
        "options": {
          "content": "# 🔧 Criar Slice via API\n\n## Via LNP (Linguagem Natural)\n```bash\ncurl -X POST http://192.168.10.16:8092/api/v1/slices \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"description\": \"Criar slice URLLC com latência de 1ms e banda de 100Mbps\"}'\n```\n\n## Via Template\n```bash\ncurl -X POST http://192.168.10.16:8092/api/v1/slices \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"slice_type\": \"${slice_type}\",\n    \"bandwidth\": ${bandwidth},\n    \"latency\": ${latency},\n    \"description\": \"Slice criado via template\"\n  }'\n```\n\n## 🔗 Links Rápidos\n- [UI TriSLA Portal](http://192.168.10.16:8092) - Interface web completa\n- [API Docs](http://192.168.10.16:8092/docs) - Documentação Swagger\n- [Health Check](http://192.168.10.16:8092/api/v1/health) - Status da API",
          "mode": "markdown"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 2,
        "title": "Slices Criados Recentemente",
        "type": "table",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 6},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "trisla_slices_created_total",
            "refId": "A",
            "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
            "format": "table",
            "instant": true
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "showHeader": true,
          "sortBy": [{"desc": true, "displayName": "Value"}]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 3,
        "title": "Status da Criação",
        "type": "stat",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 6},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "rate(trisla_slices_created_total[5m])",
            "refId": "A",
            "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"}
          },
          {
            "expr": "rate(trisla_jobs_completed_total{job=\"trisla-portal\"}[5m])",
            "refId": "B",
            "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"}
          },
          {
            "expr": "rate(trisla_jobs_failed_total{job=\"trisla-portal\"}[5m])",
            "refId": "C",
            "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"}
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": 4,
        "title": "Templates Disponíveis",
        "type": "text",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 14},
        "options": {
          "content": "## 📋 Templates de Slices\n\n### URLLC Template\n```json\n{\n  \"slice_type\": \"URLLC\",\n  \"bandwidth\": 100,\n  \"latency\": 1,\n  \"description\": \"Template URLLC\"\n}\n```\n\n### eMBB Template\n```json\n{\n  \"slice_type\": \"eMBB\",\n  \"bandwidth\": 500,\n  \"latency\": 5,\n  \"description\": \"Template eMBB\"\n}\n```\n\n### mMTC Template\n```json\n{\n  \"slice_type\": \"mMTC\",\n  \"bandwidth\": 50,\n  \"latency\": 10,\n  \"description\": \"Template mMTC\"\n}\n```",
          "mode": "markdown"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 5,
        "title": "Distribuição de Slices por Tipo",
        "type": "piechart",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 22},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum by (slice_type) (trisla_slices_active{slice_type=~\"URLLC|eMBB|mMTC\"})",
            "refId": "A",
            "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
            "legendFormat": "{{slice_type}}"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": 6,
        "title": "Tendência de Criação",
        "type": "timeseries",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 22},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "rate(trisla_slices_created_total[1h])",
            "refId": "A",
            "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
            "legendFormat": "Taxa de Criação"
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "time": {
      "from": "now-6h",
      "to": "now"
    }
  }
}




